channel.title: Help with Server Status page
channel.description:
Yes, ive looked at CopyRight's guide to the server status page.
Everytime i type everything it in. i get this
The server ToyScape (Silabs) is offline, it must be online before you can register it.
But, it is online, because i am on it with my bro atm, and im not on the comp that i have the server running, the comps have 2 different IP's.
